e=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xwo1689059556118.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xwo1689059556118.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xwo1689059556118.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xwo1689059556118\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The following sub-topics explains various supported license type options:</p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xwo1689059556118__ul_rsq_nj2_cyb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xwo1689059556118__li_d49763e1_d49764e1_d49765e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uzx1689059617149.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uzx1689059617149.html\" title=\"This option specifies the location of a license.\">LM_LICENSE_FILE</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xwo1689059556118__li_d49769e1_d49770e1_d49771e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bom1689059650753.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bom1689059650753.html\" title=\"This option displays various notification messages in the transcript window and log file, starting from the NumberOfDays before the license expiry date.\">LM_TRANSCRIPT</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ars1689059701075.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ars1689059701075.html\" title=\"This option displays various notification messages in the log file, starting from the NumberOfDays before the license expiry date.\">LM_LOGFILE</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xwo1689059556118__li_d49766e1_d49767e1_d49768e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bcz1689059735580.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bcz1689059735580.html\" title=\"This option determines the notification period before a Uniface license expires. During this period, Uniface displays a notification message in a dialog box every time the application is started (unless this option is set to 0 or LM_NOTIFY_EXPIRATION=postmessage).\">LM_NOTIFICATION</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xwo1689059556118__li_d49772e1_d49773e1_d49774e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sca1689059756273.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sca1689059756273.html\" title=\"This option determines the notification period before a Uniface license lease needs to be renewed (by connecting to the internet). During this period, Uniface displays a notification message in a dialog box every time the application is started (unless this option is set to 0 or LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE is set).\">LM_RENEWAL_NOTIFICATION</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rcn1690339726415.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rcn1690339726415.html\" title=\"This option determines the notification period before a Uniface commuter license lease needs to be renewed (by connecting to the internet). During this period, Uniface displays a notification message in a postmessage, transcript window, message box, or log file (unless this option is set to 0 or LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE is set).\">LM_COMMUTER_NOTIFICATION</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fqo1690339679471.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fqo1690339679471.html\" title=\"This option determines the notification period before a Uniface application version needs to be upgraded to a currently supported version. During this period, Uniface displays a notification message in a postmessage, transcript window, message box, or log file (unless this option is set to 0 or LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE is set).\">LM_UPGRADE_NOTIFICATION</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xwo1689059556118__li_d49775e1_d49776e1_d49777e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eot1689059936048.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eot1689059936048.html\" title=\"This option determines the notification period before a Uniface feature reaches its maintenance expiry date. By default, this option is set to 0, and no warning messages are displayed. If set to a value greater than 0, Uniface displays a notification message in a dialog box every time the application is started (unless LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE is set).\">LM_MAINTENANCE_NOTIFICATION</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xwo1689059556118__li_d49778e1_d49779e1_d49780e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fgi1689059963417.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgi1689059963417.html\" title=\"If specified, this option suppresses the default message and sends an asynchronous message to the Uniface application, enabling it to provide customized handling of the expiration notice.\">LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xwo1689059556118__li_d49781e1_d49782e1_d49783e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"naa1689059984146.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/naa1689059984146.html\" title=\"This option specifies how Uniface tries to check out Sentinel licenses.\">LM_LOAD</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hya1712054931493.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hya1712054931493.html\" title=\"The LM_REDUNDANT setting is used when you have a pool of redundant RMS servers and Uniface experiences delays of several seconds when it acquires its licenses from this pool.\">LM_REDUNDANT</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xzo1697451500520.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xzo1697451500520.html\" title=\"The default timeout to connect to a Sentinel RMS server is 30 seconds. If the RMS server does not respond within that time, Uniface will stop trying and report an error. But 30 seconds may be too long or too short, so LM_TIMEOUT can be used to set a different timeout (in seconds).\">LM_TIMEOUT</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4402337\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4402337\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "License options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The following sub-topics explains various supported license type options: LM_LICENSE_FILE LM_TRANSCRIPT LM_LOGFILE LM_NOTIFICATION LM_RENEWAL_NOTIFICATION LM_COMMUTER_NOTIFICATION LM_UPGRADE_NOTIFICATION LM_MAINTENANCE_NOTIFICATION LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE LM_LOAD LM_REDUNDANT LM_TIMEOUT Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}